WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:47.239 --> 00:01:48.719
We don't engage in petty fights.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:50.680
We arrest,

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.120
or we kill.

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:56.799
You're interested in me too, right?

00:01:58.519 --> 00:01:59.120
Get out.

00:02:01.319 --> 00:02:01.719
Out!

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:02.799
Now!

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:05.480
Don't tell others

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:08.879
I only have three years left.

00:02:09.879 --> 00:02:11.280
Please keep this secret for me.

00:03:02.800 --> 00:03:03.560
Auntie,

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:13.680
this is a letter

00:03:14.199 --> 00:03:15.039
from Xian.

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:48.719
[Sis,]

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.439
[the northern steppe army will reach]

00:03:51.439 --> 00:03:52.439
[Huxiao Gorge in a few hours.]

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.560
[Only now did it hit me]

00:03:56.199 --> 00:03:57.319
[that I forgot to say goodbye]

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:59.240
[to you and Mom before leaving this time.]

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:05.800
[So I'm writing this in a hurry.]

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.520
[If I die in battle,]

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:10.039
[at least I have left you these words.]

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:13.360
[You must be wondering]

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.080
[how I could possibly die in battle.]

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:17.279
[Honestly, I still don't know myself]

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:19.600
[how I ended up]

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:20.680
[commanding troops here.]

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:22.879
[But I have to say,]

00:04:23.639 --> 00:04:24.480
[the Ye family name]
[still carries weight.]

00:04:26.199 --> 00:04:27.360
[Seeing the Flying Tiger Flag,]

00:04:28.519 --> 00:04:29.079
[hundreds of soldiers']

00:04:29.079 --> 00:04:30.160
[morale surged.]

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:34.279
[Father spent decades guarding the frontier.]

00:04:34.519 --> 00:04:35.519
[It wasn't for nothing.]

00:04:37.959 --> 00:04:38.519
[By the way,]

00:04:39.319 --> 00:04:40.519
[if I die,]

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.360
[please don't cry.]

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:45.319
[Before I left the capital,]

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:46.839
[the doctor told me]

00:04:47.879 --> 00:04:49.319
[I had three years left at most.]

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:51.800
[Anyway,]

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:53.519
[dying in battle]

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:54.639
[is better than]

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:55.920
[waiting for death to come in bed.]

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.319
[And don't blame Jinzhao.]

00:05:03.639 --> 00:05:04.879
[I came with her]

00:05:06.079 --> 00:05:06.879
[because I wanted]
[to see the frontier]

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:09.759
[while I still could,]

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:11.240
[to see]

00:05:11.240 --> 00:05:12.800
[the battlefield]

00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:14.439
[Dad always talked about.]

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:17.839
[Now I have.]

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:20.279
[It's right in front of me.]

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:23.759
[Sis,]

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.519
[words fail me.]

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:28.720
[I cannot describe]

00:05:28.839 --> 00:05:30.160
[how vast and boundless the world is.]

00:05:32.519 --> 00:05:33.160
[But I know]

00:05:33.879 --> 00:05:35.439
[this is where I was meant to be.]

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:39.759
[If Father]

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:40.959
[heard me]

00:05:41.240 --> 00:05:42.399
[say that,]

00:05:42.959 --> 00:05:44.319
[would he be proud?]

00:05:45.519 --> 00:05:46.759
[Though even if he were still alive,]

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:48.560
[I'd never admit it]
[to his face.]

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:50.920
[After all,]

00:05:50.920 --> 00:05:52.040
[he used to beat me so hard.]

00:05:53.279 --> 00:05:54.720
[He only ever doted on you,]

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:56.360
[never on me.]

00:05:57.439 --> 00:05:58.160
[But that's alright.]

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.040
[When I die]

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.079
[and see him again,]

00:06:01.399 --> 00:06:02.160
[I'll tell him not to]

00:06:03.279 --> 00:06:05.040
[boast about how great he was in battle.]

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:06.399
[I've fought in one too.]

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:09.519
[Alright,]

00:06:10.279 --> 00:06:11.519
[I shall discuss battle plans with Yanyun.]

00:06:12.199 --> 00:06:13.439
[This time I'm the commander.]

00:06:13.839 --> 00:06:14.600
[He's my deputy.]

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:38.319
How dare you!

00:06:39.199 --> 00:06:40.319
This is the Gallowspass

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:42.519
granted by the late Emperor himself.

00:06:43.399 --> 00:06:44.759
You dare stop me?

00:06:57.279 --> 00:06:58.600
[If I don't make it back,]

00:07:00.279 --> 00:07:00.920
[please]

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:03.199
[take care of Mom for me.]

00:07:04.600 --> 00:07:05.680
[Tell her]

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:07.519
[I didn't disgrace our family.]

00:07:07.959 --> 00:07:09.360
[Nor did I let her down.]

00:07:10.079 --> 00:07:11.680
[And tell her not to be sad.]

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.519
I'm Lady He, wife of Lord Changxing.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.360
I humbly kneel before Your Majesty.

00:07:31.279 --> 00:07:32.399
The northern steppe cavalry is invading.

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:33.800
The frontier is thrown into chaos.

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:36.240
My son, Ye Xian,

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.240
and the soldiers

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:39.480
are risking their lives to hold Yi County.

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:41.519
If Yi County falls,

00:07:42.079 --> 00:07:44.399
enemies can reach the capital in three days.

00:07:44.399 --> 00:07:45.759
Our country is in danger!

00:07:46.399 --> 00:07:47.480
I come today with

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:50.199
the Gallowspass granted by the late Emperor

00:07:50.519 --> 00:07:51.560
and beg Your Majesty

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:52.920
to send reinforcements at once.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:55.279
Please save the frontier cities

00:07:55.519 --> 00:07:56.879
and save the people!

00:07:57.399 --> 00:07:58.399
We beg Your Majesty to

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.519
send reinforcements immediately!

00:07:59.959 --> 00:08:01.199
Save the frontier

00:08:01.439 --> 00:08:02.959
and our people!

00:08:15.279 --> 00:08:16.439
They're appealing to His Majesty in person.

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:18.680
Northern Barbarians are attacking Yi County?

00:08:19.079 --> 00:08:20.160
That's true.

00:08:20.519 --> 00:08:22.199
Then Men Plateau and Shi City have fallen.

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:23.800
We must strike back.

00:08:23.879 --> 00:08:24.720
Exactly.

00:08:25.839 --> 00:08:26.519
Your Majesty,

00:08:26.759 --> 00:08:28.000
if the enemy hadn't reached Yi County,

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:29.360
why would Lady Ye

00:08:29.519 --> 00:08:31.079
bring the Gallowspass

00:08:31.279 --> 00:08:32.320
and plead for aid?

00:08:33.159 --> 00:08:33.960
I think

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.399
the army has asked for reinforcements,

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:38.679
but someone

00:08:38.840 --> 00:08:40.279
with ulterior motives has

00:08:40.279 --> 00:08:41.279
suppressed the letter.

00:08:48.879 --> 00:08:49.360
Your Majesty,

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:51.360
do not believe such nonsense.

00:08:51.519 --> 00:08:52.960
Mrs. Ye entered the palace without permission

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:53.960
and should be punished.

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:56.840
Your Majesty,

00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:58.080
it's better

00:08:58.639 --> 00:09:00.240
to summon Lady Ye and her daughter

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:01.519
into the hall, question them,

00:09:01.799 --> 00:09:03.120
and send someone to Bureau of Transmission

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:04.200
to check whether

00:09:04.399 --> 00:09:05.639
any letters came from the frontier.

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:06.559
Then all

00:09:07.039 --> 00:09:07.879
will be clear.

00:09:10.679 --> 00:09:12.240
You're right.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:13.840
Bring them in.

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:43.879
Greetings,

00:09:44.279 --> 00:09:45.519
Your Majesty.

00:09:50.039 --> 00:09:50.759
Mrs. Ye,

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:53.639
the words you spoke outside the hall,

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:55.000
who taught you to say them?

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:56.639
Your Majesty,

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.399
no one.

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:00.600
My son, Ye Xian, is doing everything

00:10:00.879 --> 00:10:02.000
he can to hold the frontier,

00:10:02.159 --> 00:10:03.759
but reinforcements never came.

00:10:04.519 --> 00:10:05.080
So he

00:10:05.879 --> 00:10:08.000
had to write to me for help.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:09.720
The letter

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:11.360
will speak for itself, Your Majesty.

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:26.080
[Your subject, Ye Xian,]

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:27.679
[pays his respect.]

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:29.879
[Northern Barbarians attacked suddenly.]

00:10:30.039 --> 00:10:30.759
[Shi City]

00:10:31.039 --> 00:10:31.919
[and Men Plateau have fallen.]

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:33.080
[The border defenses have collapsed,]

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:35.159
[and Yi County hangs by a thread.]

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:37.159
[Yanyun and I]

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:38.519
[are trying to hold them off,]

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:40.399
[but we're badly outnumbered.]

00:10:41.039 --> 00:10:43.000
[Please dispatch reinforcements at once.]

00:10:43.759 --> 00:10:44.440
[Should I die,]

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:45.600
[I have no regrets.]

00:10:46.799 --> 00:10:48.519
[May the Great Yan prosper, and the people]

00:10:49.639 --> 00:10:50.879
[live in peace for eternity.]

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:05.240
Show this letter

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.279
to the ministers.

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:23.840
Mrs. Ye,

00:11:25.159 --> 00:11:25.840
I believe

00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:26.759
you.

00:11:27.559 --> 00:11:28.639
Thanks, Your Majesty.

00:11:30.039 --> 00:11:30.600
Your Majesty...
Mr. Fu,

00:11:32.799 --> 00:11:34.559
if you hadn't insisted on cutting

00:11:35.120 --> 00:11:36.240
the military funding,

00:11:37.159 --> 00:11:39.519
none of this would have happened.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:41.440
The situation

00:11:42.559 --> 00:11:44.399
at the border is critical.

00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:46.159
We must dispatch troops at once

00:11:46.399 --> 00:11:47.440
to reinforce the front line.

00:11:47.679 --> 00:11:48.960
As for provisions and weapons,

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:51.279
I'll pay for them from my own pocket.

00:11:51.919 --> 00:11:53.360
Who will step forward

00:11:53.639 --> 00:11:55.360
and lead the army

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.000
into battle?

00:11:57.799 --> 00:11:58.679
I will!

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:00.519
I will!
I will!

00:12:01.519 --> 00:12:02.159
I will!

00:12:02.679 --> 00:12:04.399
I will!

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:05.720
Nonsense.

00:12:06.919 --> 00:12:07.679
Your Majesty,

00:12:08.559 --> 00:12:10.080
mobilizing troops

00:12:10.440 --> 00:12:12.080
is no trivial matter.

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:14.000
A suitable commander must be

00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:16.000
nominated by the Ministry of War

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:18.320
and appointed after deliberation.

00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:19.159
How can they

00:12:20.399 --> 00:12:22.399
just volunteer for the role?

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:25.919
The situation is this dire,

00:12:26.080 --> 00:12:27.320
and you still stick to procedures?

00:12:27.639 --> 00:12:29.200
You're stalling on purpose!

00:12:29.559 --> 00:12:30.399
How dare you!

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:32.600
You're the one who has gone too far!

00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:38.120
Your Majesty, please don't be mad.

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:09.879
Yanyun!

00:13:18.759 --> 00:13:19.879
[There's a wooden box]

00:13:20.960 --> 00:13:22.200
[behind the painting in the study.]

00:13:23.120 --> 00:13:23.759
[Inside]

00:13:23.759 --> 00:13:25.360
[are the things I treasure most.]

00:13:27.759 --> 00:13:28.840
[If I...]

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:33.799
[Keep them as something to remember me by.]

00:14:20.279 --> 00:14:21.039
It's getting cold.

00:14:54.519 --> 00:14:55.519
[Green willow branches hang low,]

00:14:56.240 --> 00:14:57.279
[Begonia flowers bloom.]

00:14:58.519 --> 00:14:59.639
[My heart belongs to you,]

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:01.399
[May my dream someday come true.]

00:15:04.519 --> 00:15:06.159
[In the autumn of Jingning Era's 35th year,]

00:15:06.639 --> 00:15:08.759
[I painted this in longing for Jinzhao.]

00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:10.639
[I never thought she]

00:15:11.120 --> 00:15:12.120
[would one day marry me.]

00:15:19.000 --> 00:15:20.279
[I must hide this at once.]

00:15:21.080 --> 00:15:22.440
[If Jinzhao saw it,]

00:15:23.240 --> 00:15:24.679
[she'd laugh at me for being a fool.]

00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:26.360
[Remember this.]

00:15:27.080 --> 00:15:27.799
[Remember.]

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:30.000
[Autumn, the Second Year of the Shengde Era.]

00:15:53.440 --> 00:15:53.960
Miss,

00:16:00.360 --> 00:16:01.679
what are you doing here?

00:16:03.919 --> 00:16:04.919
Nothing.

00:16:06.519 --> 00:16:07.840
How long has it been since His Majesty

00:16:10.120 --> 00:16:11.559
ordered to dispatch reinforcements?

00:16:12.320 --> 00:16:13.279
Five days.

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:17.039
I've been

00:16:18.039 --> 00:16:19.159
asking around.

00:16:20.639 --> 00:16:21.720
The Ministry of War says

00:16:23.320 --> 00:16:24.519
before 50,000 troops can march,

00:16:25.799 --> 00:16:27.360
civil laborers need to be gathered.

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:29.039
That alone takes days.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:31.279
And the supply lines

00:16:33.279 --> 00:16:34.440
aren't ready either.

00:16:35.399 --> 00:16:36.440
And I've heard that

00:16:37.519 --> 00:16:39.320
though Fu Hailian is under house arrest,

00:16:41.039 --> 00:16:42.399
his people still hold key positions

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:43.279
across the Six Ministries.

00:16:45.159 --> 00:16:46.679
One word from him,

00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:49.759
and they'll find every way to stall.

00:16:53.519 --> 00:16:54.360
I see.

00:17:02.039 --> 00:17:03.360
Go tell Yao

00:17:04.039 --> 00:17:05.359
to find Mr. Ping.

00:17:05.920 --> 00:17:06.519
Tonight,

00:17:07.319 --> 00:17:08.880
leave the capital

00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:11.119
with the Chen family.

00:17:12.400 --> 00:17:13.359
Don't bring anything.

00:17:14.160 --> 00:17:14.960
It will

00:17:15.960 --> 00:17:17.079
only draw suspicion.

00:17:18.839 --> 00:17:20.160
Yao knows where to go.

00:17:21.519 --> 00:17:22.559
Go with them and keep them safe.

00:17:23.640 --> 00:17:24.240
Miss...

00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:25.440
Let me finish.

00:17:28.119 --> 00:17:29.039
You have good martial skills.

00:17:30.839 --> 00:17:32.400
I need you to protect the Chen family.

00:17:34.279 --> 00:17:35.319
If Fu Hailian

00:17:35.720 --> 00:17:36.839
sends the troops

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:39.559
and saves Yanyun,

00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:41.720
come back

00:17:42.440 --> 00:17:43.720
to the capital with them.

00:17:47.319 --> 00:17:48.400
If he doesn't,

00:17:51.319 --> 00:17:52.759
don't come back.

00:17:55.279 --> 00:17:56.200
I burned your

00:17:56.599 --> 00:17:57.799
indentured servitude contract long ago.

00:17:59.160 --> 00:18:00.880
I've also bought several properties for you.

00:18:02.119 --> 00:18:02.880
The deeds

00:18:03.319 --> 00:18:04.559
are with Mr. Ping.

00:18:06.319 --> 00:18:07.240
He'll give them to you.

00:18:10.559 --> 00:18:11.039
Miss,

00:18:12.119 --> 00:18:13.039
Mr. Ji

00:18:14.680 --> 00:18:16.079
will take care of the Chen family.

00:18:19.119 --> 00:18:20.440
Please don't leave me behind.

00:18:21.359 --> 00:18:22.759
I want to help you.

00:18:34.960 --> 00:18:36.000
I just

00:18:37.839 --> 00:18:39.039
had a terrible dream.

00:18:40.599 --> 00:18:42.000
They say dreams mean the opposite,

00:18:45.079 --> 00:18:45.920
so I

00:18:47.279 --> 00:18:48.720
believe it's a good omen.

00:19:00.519 --> 00:19:01.880
It's not that I don't want your help.

00:19:04.039 --> 00:19:05.400
You can't help with

00:19:07.519 --> 00:19:08.200
what I'm gonna do.

00:19:20.359 --> 00:19:21.119
I've

00:19:22.359 --> 00:19:23.880
treated you like my own sister.

00:19:26.079 --> 00:19:27.079
I've shared

00:19:27.799 --> 00:19:29.160
everything with you.

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:34.559
Now I'm entrusting the Chen family

00:19:35.039 --> 00:19:35.680
to you.

00:19:37.119 --> 00:19:38.279
Don't let me down.

00:19:39.839 --> 00:19:40.480
Miss...
Let her go.

00:19:46.839 --> 00:19:48.319
He was always afraid of being alone,

00:19:48.599 --> 00:19:50.119
so I stayed with him a while longer.

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:52.200
Jinzhao,

00:19:54.160 --> 00:19:55.079
he's done

00:19:55.680 --> 00:19:56.640
everything he could.

00:19:58.359 --> 00:19:59.599
The rest is up to us now.

00:20:00.400 --> 00:20:01.079
Go do what you
need to do.

00:20:02.759 --> 00:20:03.799
As long as I'm here,

00:20:04.519 --> 00:20:06.079
no one can touch that coffin

00:20:06.440 --> 00:20:07.759
or the Chen family.

00:20:09.759 --> 00:20:10.359
Thank you.

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:16.680
Stop.

00:22:00.519 --> 00:22:02.440
I thought you came here

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:03.880
looking for a fight.

00:22:09.319 --> 00:22:10.240
This is poison.

00:22:11.359 --> 00:22:12.240
If you send troops

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:13.640
to the frontier now,

00:22:14.759 --> 00:22:15.519
I will

00:22:16.119 --> 00:22:17.279
drink it.

00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:38.079
I'm under house arrest.

00:22:38.559 --> 00:22:39.559
What power

00:22:39.559 --> 00:22:41.160
do I have to send troops?

00:22:42.799 --> 00:22:44.279
You've come to the wrong person,

00:22:44.559 --> 00:22:45.400
Mrs. Chen.

00:22:46.880 --> 00:22:48.680
Your Excellency, I once

00:22:49.160 --> 00:22:50.160
offended you

00:22:50.920 --> 00:22:51.880
and drew a sword against you.

00:22:52.839 --> 00:22:54.119
I deserve to die for that.

00:23:02.039 --> 00:23:03.440
Now that Yanyun is dead,

00:23:05.119 --> 00:23:06.160
I have nothing

00:23:06.839 --> 00:23:07.880
left to live for.

00:23:09.160 --> 00:23:10.519
But before I die,

00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:13.279
I beg you to

00:23:14.759 --> 00:23:15.960
set aside what's past

00:23:16.799 --> 00:23:17.720
and send the troops.

00:23:21.640 --> 00:23:22.559
Save

00:23:22.920 --> 00:23:23.680
the soldiers

00:23:23.680 --> 00:23:25.160
fighting at the frontier.

00:23:26.599 --> 00:23:27.359
And save

00:23:28.319 --> 00:23:30.200
the people on the brink.

00:23:38.160 --> 00:23:38.880
Even

00:23:39.519 --> 00:23:40.640
if I die now,

00:23:41.960 --> 00:23:42.960
I will be grateful.

00:24:02.079 --> 00:24:02.720
Drink it.

00:24:26.279 --> 00:24:26.960
Mr. Chen!

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:49.640
Jinzhao...

00:25:09.799 --> 00:25:10.880
Mr. Chen...

00:25:11.720 --> 00:25:12.519
Mr. Chen...

00:25:41.000 --> 00:25:41.720
[Wait for me.]

00:25:42.359 --> 00:25:43.400
[I will find a way to get]

00:25:44.119 --> 00:25:45.160
[the court to send troops.]

00:25:51.839 --> 00:25:53.599
Even if I stand alone,

00:25:53.880 --> 00:25:55.640
I'll still defend my country.

00:25:56.039 --> 00:25:56.720
I'm

00:25:57.799 --> 00:26:00.000
ready to charge

00:26:00.559 --> 00:26:02.000
one last time.

00:26:02.599 --> 00:26:04.559
Kill!

00:27:45.160 --> 00:27:45.680
Xian,

00:27:48.200 --> 00:27:49.160
do you see?

00:27:51.319 --> 00:27:52.279
We won.

00:27:57.839 --> 00:27:58.559
This victory

00:27:59.799 --> 00:28:00.920
belongs to you.

00:28:59.160 --> 00:29:00.200
Is everything ready?

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:02.640
I don't wanna go.

00:29:29.960 --> 00:29:30.759
Don't

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:35.720
be stubborn.

00:29:40.079 --> 00:29:41.359
I can't stop regretting it.

00:29:45.119 --> 00:29:46.279
I should never have

00:29:46.279 --> 00:29:48.160
believed those people in Shi City.

00:29:48.599 --> 00:29:50.200
We fell for Northern Barbarians' trick,

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.960
and your plans are ruined.

00:30:03.799 --> 00:30:04.720
You

00:30:06.839 --> 00:30:07.920
shouldn't be drinking.

00:30:09.519 --> 00:30:10.759
Have some tea instead.

00:30:21.680 --> 00:30:23.119
At this point,

00:30:24.079 --> 00:30:24.839
it's

00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:28.000
no one's fault but mine.

00:30:28.440 --> 00:30:29.119
After all,
I was too impatient

00:30:30.119 --> 00:30:30.960
and too confident.

00:30:32.279 --> 00:30:34.720
I wanted to seize

00:30:34.960 --> 00:30:36.160
all power at court.

00:30:36.359 --> 00:30:37.279
I wanted to

00:30:37.440 --> 00:30:39.920
have a firm grip on the reforms.

00:30:41.119 --> 00:30:43.160
I thought once the court was under control,

00:30:43.440 --> 00:30:45.880
Northern Barbarians' betrayal

00:30:46.279 --> 00:30:48.000
would be nothing.

00:30:48.759 --> 00:30:50.440
I thought I could read everyone

00:30:50.440 --> 00:30:51.920
and foresee everything.

00:30:51.920 --> 00:30:52.960
I didn't expect

00:30:53.079 --> 00:30:54.880
they'd turn on us so soon

00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:55.759
and act so relentlessly.

00:31:02.839 --> 00:31:04.839
Fate isn't on my side.

00:31:21.279 --> 00:31:23.079
Sorry to drag you into it.

00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:30.759
We're married for 20 years,

00:31:34.359 --> 00:31:36.319
but I never gave you a child.

00:31:37.519 --> 00:31:38.720
You never blamed me

00:31:40.519 --> 00:31:41.960
and never even took a concubine.

00:31:46.400 --> 00:31:47.599
You've treated me well,

00:31:49.119 --> 00:31:51.160
and I'm willing to die with you.

00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:54.599
I took no concubines

00:31:55.079 --> 00:31:56.039
and had no children

00:31:56.039 --> 00:31:57.720
for a reason.

00:31:59.759 --> 00:32:00.880
I knew

00:32:02.440 --> 00:32:03.759
danger lay ahead,

00:32:05.319 --> 00:32:06.640
so I didn't want...

00:32:07.319 --> 00:32:08.519
No matter what you say,

00:32:12.599 --> 00:32:13.559
I'm not leaving

00:32:13.559 --> 00:32:14.680
without you.

00:32:32.400 --> 00:32:32.880
Go.

00:32:36.680 --> 00:32:37.160
Your Excellency.

00:32:54.440 --> 00:32:55.319
Take good care of Mrs. Fu.

00:32:55.839 --> 00:32:56.599
Yes.

00:33:04.599 --> 00:33:05.119
Your Excellency,

00:33:05.960 --> 00:33:06.559
I'm

00:33:07.519 --> 00:33:08.400
a bit confused.

00:33:11.960 --> 00:33:13.240
You wanna know

00:33:13.240 --> 00:33:15.720
why I agreed to send troops?

00:33:16.319 --> 00:33:18.440
Not because she begged me,

00:33:20.359 --> 00:33:21.720
but because of Great Yan!

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:29.839
Everything I've done all these years

00:33:30.119 --> 00:33:31.279
has been for the reforms.

00:33:32.640 --> 00:33:34.039
What use are reforms

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:40.200
if the nation falls?

00:33:46.480 --> 00:33:47.039
I

00:33:48.640 --> 00:33:49.240
understand.

00:33:51.000 --> 00:33:51.599
Your Excellency,

00:33:52.240 --> 00:33:53.079
what do you plan

00:33:53.640 --> 00:33:54.400
to do with Mrs. Chen?

00:34:00.200 --> 00:34:01.319
Keep her here for now.

00:34:03.039 --> 00:34:04.319
As long as she's alive,

00:34:05.400 --> 00:34:07.279
he will come to see me.

00:34:09.920 --> 00:34:10.320
Yes.

00:34:31.880 --> 00:34:33.360
Why did you stop me?

00:34:35.519 --> 00:34:36.960
What use would your death

00:34:36.960 --> 00:34:37.719
be to me?

00:34:43.119 --> 00:34:44.880
If all goes as expected,

00:34:46.440 --> 00:34:47.320
Yanyun

00:34:47.920 --> 00:34:50.280
will reach the capital tonight.

00:34:53.880 --> 00:34:55.119
You knew he was alive?

00:34:55.760 --> 00:34:57.880
Of all the students in my life,

00:34:59.079 --> 00:35:01.079
he's the one most like me.

00:35:02.159 --> 00:35:04.280
He wouldn't die so easily.

00:35:07.400 --> 00:35:08.519
It's good, though.

00:35:09.679 --> 00:35:10.840
He may find a way

00:35:12.039 --> 00:35:13.519
out of the deadlock.

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:20.119
You spared me

00:35:21.000 --> 00:35:22.440
to use me against him?

00:35:28.639 --> 00:35:29.519
Zhang Qi.

00:35:33.800 --> 00:35:34.280
Your Excellency.

00:35:35.400 --> 00:35:37.840
Send her back.

00:35:42.519 --> 00:35:43.920
As I said,

00:35:45.000 --> 00:35:46.440
your death is of no use

00:35:47.079 --> 00:35:47.800
to me.

00:35:50.880 --> 00:35:51.320
Yes.

00:35:53.400 --> 00:35:54.000
Mrs. Chen,

00:35:56.159 --> 00:35:56.679
this way.

00:36:30.039 --> 00:36:31.679
He should be back by now.

00:36:39.360 --> 00:36:40.199
Where is Jinzhao?

00:36:43.119 --> 00:36:45.880
Essential Instructions for New Policies,

00:36:47.280 --> 00:36:49.039
this book contains

00:36:50.039 --> 00:36:51.559
everything I've learned

00:36:51.880 --> 00:36:52.840
from over

00:36:52.840 --> 00:36:53.880
a decade of reform.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:57.440
What a masterpiece.

00:36:58.079 --> 00:36:59.719
The Great Yan's stood for 120 years.

00:36:59.719 --> 00:37:01.039
Of so many men

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:03.760
who held power,

00:37:04.119 --> 00:37:05.760
nobles or ministers,

00:37:05.920 --> 00:37:08.679
who could match my talent?

00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:10.280
And who

00:37:10.440 --> 00:37:12.679
is as loyal as me?

00:37:16.119 --> 00:37:17.239
Yanyun,

00:37:17.360 --> 00:37:20.199
do you think I get what I deserve?

00:37:20.559 --> 00:37:21.400
Fu Hailian,

00:37:21.800 --> 00:37:23.159
you're so arrogant.

00:37:24.119 --> 00:37:25.639
How pathetic.

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:27.719
To govern is to serve the people,

00:37:28.280 --> 00:37:29.400
regardless of personal gains.

00:37:30.119 --> 00:37:31.360
Have you forgotten

00:37:32.360 --> 00:37:33.880
what you once stood for?

00:37:34.719 --> 00:37:37.199
Regardless of personal gains?

00:37:37.840 --> 00:37:39.519
How naive.

00:37:40.440 --> 00:37:41.559
If I hadn't calculated everything,

00:37:41.559 --> 00:37:42.440
how could I

00:37:42.719 --> 00:37:43.960
have risen

00:37:43.960 --> 00:37:45.199
this far?

00:37:46.199 --> 00:37:47.760
How would the tax reforms

00:37:48.519 --> 00:37:50.800
have ever been carried through?

00:37:51.079 --> 00:37:51.840
Yanyun,

00:37:52.119 --> 00:37:53.639
you just don't get it.

00:37:53.800 --> 00:37:55.719
That's why you turned against me.

00:37:56.719 --> 00:37:57.599
Fine.

00:37:57.920 --> 00:37:58.599
Fine.

00:37:59.119 --> 00:37:59.880
At this point,

00:37:59.880 --> 00:38:01.360
I'm finished,

00:38:01.920 --> 00:38:03.119
and the reforms are over.

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:04.239
So no one
walks out

00:38:05.559 --> 00:38:06.519
of here alive today.

00:38:06.719 --> 00:38:08.440
Die with me.

00:38:08.960 --> 00:38:10.199
The reforms are not over.

00:38:12.039 --> 00:38:13.199
Some of them

00:38:13.199 --> 00:38:14.199
may have gone too far,

00:38:14.639 --> 00:38:15.519
but most of them are

00:38:15.719 --> 00:38:17.239
sound policies for governing this nation.

00:38:18.679 --> 00:38:20.239
The problem was you.

00:38:22.440 --> 00:38:22.880
Tell me

00:38:23.519 --> 00:38:24.400
where Jinzhao is.

00:38:37.360 --> 00:38:38.119
Chen Yanyun!

00:38:42.199 --> 00:38:42.880
Put the sword down.

00:38:43.639 --> 00:38:44.320
Yuzhu?

00:38:44.880 --> 00:38:46.159
Why are you here?

00:38:46.559 --> 00:38:47.320
What do you want?

00:38:47.800 --> 00:38:48.559
Let him go.

00:38:49.519 --> 00:38:50.840
I'm the Chunyuan Sect Master.

00:38:51.360 --> 00:38:52.880
Everything was my doing.

00:38:53.320 --> 00:38:54.239
It has

00:38:54.599 --> 00:38:55.880
nothing to do with him.

00:38:56.119 --> 00:38:57.880
Why are you doing this?

00:38:58.800 --> 00:38:59.519
Hailian,

00:39:01.440 --> 00:39:02.719
how can I

00:39:02.719 --> 00:39:04.159
watch you die?

00:39:05.119 --> 00:39:06.119
Just leave.

00:39:06.400 --> 00:39:07.119
No.

00:39:27.679 --> 00:39:28.360
Hai...

00:39:28.840 --> 00:39:29.400
Hailian...

00:39:44.400 --> 00:39:45.000
Are you okay?

00:39:45.599 --> 00:39:46.280
Did you get hurt?

00:39:46.719 --> 00:39:47.519
Yanyun.

00:39:50.199 --> 00:39:50.960
I'm late.

00:40:00.559 --> 00:40:01.639
Hailian...

00:40:05.880 --> 00:40:06.760
Yuzhu.

00:40:13.800 --> 00:40:14.719
Yuzhu?

00:40:24.519 --> 00:40:25.800
Yuzhu...

00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:31.719
[Fu Hailian,]

00:40:32.400 --> 00:40:33.360
[I will]

00:40:33.360 --> 00:40:34.960
[never repeat your mistakes.]

00:40:36.199 --> 00:40:37.719
[I'll always have faith]

00:40:38.880 --> 00:40:41.000
[and stick to principles.]

00:42:04.239 --> 00:42:07.639
[By Heaven's Mandate, the Emperor decrees:]

00:42:08.159 --> 00:42:09.760
[the treacherous Chunyuan Sect]

00:42:09.880 --> 00:42:11.239
[deceived the people,]

00:42:11.360 --> 00:42:12.800
[defied the moral order,]

00:42:12.960 --> 00:42:14.360
[stirred up rebellion,]

00:42:14.519 --> 00:42:15.880
[and inflicted suffering upon people.]

00:42:16.199 --> 00:42:17.639
[Their crimes are beyond measure]

00:42:17.880 --> 00:42:19.360
[and shall not be pardoned.]

00:42:19.800 --> 00:42:23.000
[Now, the culprits have all been executed,]

00:42:23.159 --> 00:42:25.320
[and the remnants have been eradicated.]

00:42:25.880 --> 00:42:27.840
[I hope people of Great Yan henceforth]

00:42:28.000 --> 00:42:29.440
[abide by the laws,]

00:42:29.719 --> 00:42:31.199
[distinguish right from wrong,]

00:42:31.199 --> 00:42:32.519
[stay from heterodox]

00:42:32.800 --> 00:42:35.239
[and delusive teachings,]

00:42:35.239 --> 00:42:37.440
[lest they incur ruin upon themselves.]

00:42:37.920 --> 00:42:39.440
[This proclamation is issued]

00:42:39.760 --> 00:42:41.519
[to all under Heaven.]

00:42:42.159 --> 00:42:43.920
[Thus it is decreed.]